<L>__{interior clockwork room continuous action}
<A>__{in the basement of the house, in a dark space we see a tiny pendulum within a delicate, antique set of gears come to life. as we pull away, runes of odd description come into view, etched on ivory plates, the plates attached to levers and meters standing poised, waiting... the lights in the room suddenly flicker on. we pull away from the odd bits of machinery, seeing it for what it is: a control panel of some kind. our retreating camera then becomes engulfed by what looks to be a huge set of gears, made of brass and steel, standing by. we pull out the other side of the gears, viewing the machinery's massive size, the gears works nearly fifteen feet high, dominating a room filled with pulleys and steel cable.}
